{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Fix s6-overlay init \u2014 use services.d for run script\n\nThe container needs to use s6's service directory instead of CMD.\nMoved run.sh to /etc/services.d/water-quality/run and set init: false.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
  "files": [
